FBIS4-31803 "dreeu116_b_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 BULGARIA Briefs Zhelev on Privatization Briefs Zhelev on Privatization AU1506161594 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1300 GMT 15 Jun 94 AU1506161594 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] President Zhelev invited ex-Deputy Prime Minister Valentin Karabashev, in his capacity as an expert on privatization, to give his views on the amendments to the Privatization Act that the National Assembly passed. Karabashev advised Dr. Zhelev to return the law to the National Assembly for further drafting because the approved changes contain a number of imperfections. He voiced serious objections concerning the chapter on mass privatization. After his meeting with President Zhelev, Valentin Karabashev declared that he is optimistic that the existing imperfections in the law can be removed when parliament reconsiders it.
